   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Forecast based Anticipatory Action to Strengthen Food Security and Coping Capacity of Communities-at-risk</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this project is to provide life multi-purpose cash assistance to vulnerable communities in Sunsari and Saptari in anticipation of monsoon flooding. This WFP project provides cash transfers to vulnerable households. The project provides life-saving assistance to 62,795 people, including 19,403 women, 17,118 men and 26,274 children, and 1,218 persons with disabilities.</narrative>
  </description>
